Lustre server: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/69/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/69/&lt;/a&gt; (2.4.2 RC1)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The interop testing cannot be performed due to the issue in this ticket:&lt;br/&gt;
